# 탐색적 데이터분석 (EDA)
## description
1. 결측치 처리
2. Box plot (맑은날만, 전체)
3. scatter plot  (맑은날만, 전체)
4. 이상치 제거

%pyspark

from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_dt2d, udf_dt2t

cas = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/simple.parquet')
wtob = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///weather/witlab/wtob_f.parquet')

cas.show(1)
wtob.show(1)

%pyspark

from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_delsec

cas_mdt = cas.withColumn('datetime', udf_delsec('datetime'))
wtob_mdt = wtob.withColumn('datetime', udf_delsec('datetime'))

whole = cas_mdt.join(wtob_mdt, 'datetime').cache()
whole.show()

%pyspark
def showCorrMtx(spdf, figsize=(11,11), annot=True, enable_mask=True, color="YlGnBu"):
    import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
    import numpy as np
    import seaborn as sns
    
    corr = spdf.toPandas().corr()
    mask = np.zeros_like(corr)
    mask[np.triu_indices_from(mask)] = enable_mask
    ax = plt.subplots(figsize=figsize)
    ax = sns.heatmap(corr, annot=annot, mask=mask, cmap=color)

def showCorrMtx2(corr, figsize=(11,11), annot=True, enable_mask=True, color="YlGnBu"):
    import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
    import numpy as np
    import seaborn as sns
    
    mask = np.zeros_like(corr)
    mask[np.triu_indices_from(mask)] = enable_mask
    ax = plt.subplots(figsize=figsize)
